        "text": "So to make this a realtime perma thing we would need:\n1. a slack app (or Mariano's creds) forwarding to a webhook.\n2. a cloudflare worker + queue + D2\n3. an atproto identity to post messages.\nvibed proposal <https:\/\/github.com\/tomlarkworthy\/wiki\/blob\/slack-colibri-bridge-proposal\/pages\/slack-colibri-bridge.md|here>. But have a look at the app, and have an explore of the atproto records the bot <https:\/\/atproto.at\/uri\/at:\/\/did:plc:a5yddar7vebmgjithmy4skj6|holds> (I am reusing another one I had already). I like that the Colibri app has a debug link that takes you to the atmosphere explorer for most of the concepts. Its transparent with the innards.",
